  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to compare two techniques of wound closure in open
      appendicectomies in adult patients: continuous, absorbable, intradermal suture and
      interrupted, non-absorbable sutures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
